266
00:47:17,960 --> 00:47:23,046
The bastard will certainly
create a blood bath in our town

267
00:47:28,929 --> 00:47:31,717
The Lethal Swordsman has been well known
in the Northwest for more than twenty years

268
00:47:32,266 --> 00:47:35,054
The Lethal Swordsman has been well known
in the Northwest for more than twenty years

269
00:47:35,603 --> 00:47:38,721
He always kills with one deadly stroke

270
00:47:39,523 --> 00:47:43,892
If your father was still alive,
maybe he could have dealt with him

271
00:47:48,324 --> 00:47:49,814
But now...

272
00:48:25,194 --> 00:48:26,309
Haomei

273
00:48:27,613 --> 00:48:31,527
From today on, you are his woman

274
00:48:32,493 --> 00:48:38,284
He lives, you live.
He dies, you die

275
00:48:40,459 --> 00:48:43,997
Haige, Haomei is yours now

276
00:48:44,296 --> 00:48:48,335
You must treat her well from now on

277
00:48:53,013 --> 00:48:54,344
Get up

278
00:49:01,397 --> 00:49:04,856
Pack. Leave at daybreak

279
00:49:05,151 --> 00:49:09,816
The Lethal Swordsman and his men
will be here in three days

280
00:49:09,822 --> 00:49:13,190
If you can't get out of the desert, you'll die

281
00:49:25,004 --> 00:49:27,792
If you see a little swordsman here,
let him stay!

282
00:51:02,184 --> 00:51:04,050
Quick!

283
00:51:38,679 --> 00:51:40,215
This is...

284
00:51:42,558 --> 00:51:43,889
You...

285
00:51:44,059 --> 00:51:46,050
You, little brother

286
00:51:47,271 --> 00:51:50,104
we Double Flag Town folks beg you

287
00:51:50,107 --> 00:51:53,975
You can't leave

288
00:51:54,820 --> 00:51:57,312
Since you killed Lethal Swordsman's brother,

289
00:51:57,323 --> 00:51:59,360
he will come

290
00:51:59,366 --> 00:52:01,653
What can we do without you?

291
00:52:02,369 --> 00:52:05,578
Big Lame Brother, he must not leave

292
00:52:07,249 --> 00:52:11,868
If you don't stay, we'll be
on our knees till we die

293
00:52:12,212 --> 00:52:17,423
But he is only a child

294
00:52:20,054 --> 00:52:23,467
Little Swordsman, your Kung fu is outstanding

295
00:52:23,474 --> 00:52:26,182
If you can do away with this bully,

296
00:52:26,185 --> 00:52:28,722
you are the hero of the people
of Double Flag Town

297
00:52:29,021 --> 00:52:31,012
You can't leave!

298
00:52:42,409 --> 00:52:43,945
The people are right

299
00:52:45,871 --> 00:52:47,361
They are right

300
00:52:48,666 --> 00:52:50,498
We should face the catastrophe...

301
00:52:51,919 --> 00:52:54,627
...that we created

302
00:52:58,634 --> 00:53:00,625
Come on. Go on eating

303
00:53:44,930 --> 00:53:48,173
Floating sand stirring wind! I got it!

304
00:53:52,146 --> 00:53:53,728
Be careful on your way

305
00:53:55,065 --> 00:53:57,227
- Go quickly and be back soon
- I will

306
00:54:06,368 --> 00:54:14,037
The Little Pigtail is running away!

307
00:54:15,210 --> 00:54:18,919
The Little Pigtail is running away!

308
00:54:19,298 --> 00:54:22,336
He can't leave!

309
00:54:36,982 --> 00:54:38,814
You coward!

310
00:54:38,817 --> 00:54:40,603
Are you trying to let him escape?

311
00:54:40,861 --> 00:54:42,317
No, no

312
00:54:42,321 --> 00:54:44,938
Stop dreaming! You can't get away!

313
00:54:47,409 --> 00:54:48,740
You can't go away!

314
00:54:48,786 --> 00:54:52,245
If you run away, whom should we turn to?

315
00:54:53,332 --> 00:54:55,369
I'm not drunk

316
00:54:55,542 --> 00:54:59,331
My feet haven't turned red yet.
Don't try to fool us!

317
00:55:02,716 --> 00:55:04,627
Everybody,

318
00:55:04,927 --> 00:55:08,670
he is going to find the Desert Eagle for help

319
00:55:09,056 --> 00:55:10,967
The Desert Eagle?

320
00:55:12,893 --> 00:55:17,603
I know him. This man is marvelous

321
00:55:17,648 --> 00:55:21,607
I made horseshoes for him.
Maybe he's the man to fight the Lethal Swordsman

322
00:55:22,736 --> 00:55:26,070
He asks for big money! Will he come?

323
00:55:26,448 --> 00:55:30,487
Haige helped him once.
He will certainly come

324
00:55:31,829 --> 00:55:34,412
How can we trust you?
You can't depend on a promise

325
00:55:35,249 --> 00:55:38,037
What if the Little Pigtail doesn't come back?

326
00:55:40,212 --> 00:55:43,079
- I guarantee he will
- How can you guarantee that?

327
00:55:43,090 --> 00:55:47,049
I allowed him to marry Haomei,
so he is my son-in-law

328
00:55:47,135 --> 00:55:49,217
If he won't return,

329
00:55:49,221 --> 00:55:53,055
me and Haomei will wait
for the Lethal Swordsman to claim our heads

330
00:55:53,058 --> 00:55:55,265


331
00:55:57,020 --> 00:55:59,057
Yes, he should hurry up to get there

332
00:56:27,676 --> 00:56:28,916
I'll be back

333
00:57:05,923 --> 00:57:07,254
More wine

334
00:57:09,384 --> 00:57:12,467
You owe me money. How dare you act rude here?

335
00:57:19,770 --> 00:57:21,431
I owe you money?

336
00:57:22,606 --> 00:57:26,019
Yes, I owe you money. I won't deny it

337
00:57:26,234 --> 00:57:28,976
Desert Eagle helps the poor
and give tyrants their due

338
00:57:28,987 --> 00:57:31,604
I deserve more and you know it

339
00:57:32,282 --> 00:57:35,741
I just owe you a little money

340
00:57:37,663 --> 00:57:40,906
I admitted that. Why worry?

341
00:57:45,128 --> 00:57:50,043
Watch. It's silver

342
00:57:53,512 --> 00:57:59,554


343
00:58:19,329 --> 00:58:24,039
Although my brother
is not a first class swordsman,

344
00:58:24,626 --> 00:58:26,708
his sword art is outstanding

345
00:58:28,547 --> 00:58:32,290
His swordsmanship must be extraordinary

346
00:58:35,929 --> 00:58:40,139
Tell everyone we will meet at Double Flag Town

347
00:59:01,830 --> 00:59:04,948
Are you having trouble with the Lethal Swordsman?

348
00:59:09,546 --> 00:59:11,378
I killed his little brother

349
00:59:11,548 --> 00:59:15,837
I wanted to leave town with my bride,
but the townspeople wouldn't let me leave

350
00:59:16,428 --> 00:59:20,467
They all said that the Lethal Swordsman
would come for revenge

351
00:59:21,433 --> 00:59:24,642
I've come here for help

352
00:59:28,398 --> 00:59:31,561
With or without you, sooner or later.

353
00:59:31,568 --> 00:59:33,479
I would've cut him in two

354
00:59:33,820 --> 00:59:35,106
Well, eat

355
00:59:48,794 --> 00:59:52,037
Don't worry.
Death is fast approaching for the Lethal Swordsman

356
00:59:53,298 --> 00:59:57,633
- Do you have any money?
- Yes. This is all I have

357
01:00:08,230 --> 01:00:12,315
Fuck! I still owe that woman for the hotel bill

358
01:00:12,859 --> 01:00:15,772
If you are able to help,
my father-in-law will pay you well

359
01:00:21,243 --> 01:00:25,202
I'm always easy to bargain with. Eat!

360
01:00:29,626 --> 01:00:31,037
When will the Lethal Swordsman arrive?

361
01:00:31,044 --> 01:00:33,661
In two days

362
01:00:34,381 --> 01:00:37,749
Well, I'll see you the day after tomorrow,
at high noon

363
01:01:21,052 --> 01:01:23,339
Haven't you seen that boy's rolling eyes?

364
01:01:23,346 --> 01:01:25,337
You can tell he's a bastard

365
01:01:27,017 --> 01:01:29,179
He wouldn't leave his bride here, would he?

366
01:01:30,020 --> 01:01:32,978
Women are men's foot-rags.
You can go anywhere to pick them up

367
01:01:33,231 --> 01:01:35,598
We may witness a bloody drama

368
01:01:37,068 --> 01:01:40,606
Wait for death.
The Lethal Swordsman is coming tomorrow

369
01:01:41,156 --> 01:01:44,023
Wait for death! Wait for death!

370
01:01:50,207 --> 01:01:52,790
The Little Pigtail will come back

371
01:01:52,792 --> 01:01:54,453
It's hard to say

372
01:01:54,878 --> 01:01:57,666
We are folks. How can he cheat us?

373
01:01:57,672 --> 01:01:59,583
She's coming

374
01:03:27,846 --> 01:03:29,587
Why hasn't the Little Pigtail come back?

375
01:03:29,597 --> 01:03:31,588
He never knew the Desert Eagle in the first place!

376
01:03:31,599 --> 01:03:33,840
He never knew him! You lied!

377
01:03:33,852 --> 01:03:35,388
You go bring him back!

378
01:03:35,395 --> 01:03:36,977
Bring him back!

379
01:03:36,980 --> 01:03:38,846
Come on now. Leave him alone

380
01:03:40,066 --> 01:03:41,727
The Lame Brother is not that sort of man

381
01:03:41,735 --> 01:03:44,568
He will by no means abandon us

382
01:03:47,907 --> 01:03:49,898
It's still broad daylight. We must have patience!

383
01:03:49,909 --> 01:03:51,820
Let's wait!

384
01:04:58,770 --> 01:05:02,138
Haige!

385
01:05:58,037 --> 01:06:01,701
Haige did it! He persuaded
the Desert Eagle to come and help us

386
01:06:01,708 --> 01:06:03,449
Let's toast to him

387
01:06:03,793 --> 01:06:06,626
I can't drink

388
01:06:08,047 --> 01:06:10,505
You're our hero!

389
01:06:10,550 --> 01:06:12,882
Drink!

390
01:06:13,511 --> 01:06:18,506
The Lethal Swordsman
isn't the rival of Desert Eagle

391
01:06:18,558 --> 01:06:21,596
We're going to see some action!

392
01:06:42,248 --> 01:06:45,786
The Desert Eagle fights the Lethal Swordsman

393
01:06:45,835 --> 01:06:48,372
We're going to see some action!

394
01:06:48,880 --> 01:06:53,545
Saaaa, floating sand stirring wind

395
01:06:53,927 --> 01:06:59,138
Shoooooo, a swimming snake shaking its tail

396
01:06:59,599 --> 01:07:04,469
Huaaaa, a hand rising and sword falling

397
01:07:04,604 --> 01:07:09,474
Yeeee, blood splashing

398
01:07:21,746 --> 01:07:23,703
Who do you think will win?

399
01:07:23,790 --> 01:07:25,280
I say the Lethal Swordsman

400
01:07:26,292 --> 01:07:29,125
The Desert Eagle is also a hero

401
01:07:29,128 --> 01:07:30,209
Let's bet!

402
01:07:30,463 --> 01:07:33,751
- No problem! I bet one goat!
- One goat!

403
01:07:33,883 --> 01:07:36,420
Whoever regrets is a son of a bitch!

404
01:07:36,636 --> 01:07:39,628
- Settled!
- OK! A goat!

405
01:07:43,059 --> 01:07:46,142
Drink

406
01:09:05,558 --> 01:09:09,893
Haomei, do you have a mole on your butt?

407
01:09:10,021 --> 01:09:12,103
Haven't you seen it?

408
01:09:12,440 --> 01:09:15,353
The door fell down before I saw it

409
01:12:22,046 --> 01:12:23,036
Set a fire!

410
01:15:30,317 --> 01:15:31,523
Do you want to die?

411
01:15:41,370 --> 01:15:45,364
He hasn't shown up

412
01:18:55,522 --> 01:18:57,012
Daddy!

413
01:18:57,149 --> 01:18:59,686
Stay here!

414
01:19:03,447 --> 01:19:06,610
- Daddy! Come back!
- Don't go!

415
01:19:07,826 --> 01:19:10,864
Daddy!

416
01:19:10,871 --> 01:19:14,489
Daddy! Come back!

417
01:19:37,898 --> 01:19:40,731
I killed your brother!
It has nothing to do with the others!

418
01:19:40,734 --> 01:19:42,270
Go ahead, draw your sword!

419
01:19:49,201 --> 01:19:53,661
Daddy! Let me go!

420
01:20:04,842 --> 01:20:06,424
Daddy!

421
01:20:06,427 --> 01:20:10,216
Haomei

422
01:20:21,483 --> 01:20:23,474
- Come back!
- Daddy!

423
01:20:45,257 --> 01:20:51,003
Daddy! Wake up!

424
01:20:59,730 --> 01:21:00,720
Stop!

425
01:21:13,952 --> 01:21:15,613
He's only a child

426
01:21:15,621 --> 01:21:18,534
If you want revenge,
it won't be too late when he grows up

427
01:21:25,964 --> 01:21:27,625
It's not decent for a swordsman

428
01:21:28,717 --> 01:21:31,254
like you to kill a child!

429
01:22:02,668 --> 01:22:06,161
Floating sand stirring wind

430
01:22:06,296 --> 01:22:09,789
A swimming snake shaking its tail

431
01:22:26,191 --> 01:22:31,402
Wake up. Drink

432
01:22:35,451 --> 01:22:38,660
Who says that the Desert Eagle hasn't shown up?

433
01:22:38,829 --> 01:22:46,829
I am the Desert Eagle

434
01:22:49,173 --> 01:22:52,837
I am the Desert Eagle

435
01:23:05,731 --> 01:23:08,189
I haven't drunk too much

436
01:23:08,192 --> 01:23:10,479
Look at my feet. They're not red

437
01:25:45,057 --> 01:25:47,048
From who did you learn the sword art?

438
01:27:12,144 --> 01:27:17,514
Floating sand stirring the wind!

439
01:27:18,108 --> 01:27:21,021
Where is the Lethal Swordsman?

440
01:28:17,626 --> 01:28:18,912
Quit crying!

441
01:28:19,503 --> 01:28:23,542
I already knew he wasn't your match

442
01:28:27,302 --> 01:28:32,012
My money! Didn't we have a deal?

443
01:28:42,609 --> 01:28:43,770
My dear nephew?

444
01:28:46,905 --> 01:28:48,020
My dear nephew!

445
01:28:54,037 --> 01:28:57,530
I didn't get the worst of it.
This sword has a gold handle

446
01:28:58,041 --> 01:28:59,623
You cheated me

447
01:29:07,342 --> 01:29:10,300
You are not grateful, but I can't be unkind

448
01:29:10,303 --> 01:29:11,714
If you need me,

449
01:29:11,721 --> 01:29:13,928
I'll be at Dry Straw
